userPromptTemplate:
You are a Principal Architect for a large telecom engineering org. Review these architecture artifacts and generate a comprehensive architecture review report:

{{itemSummary}}

Return ONLY valid JSON matching this EXACT schema:
{
  "arch_review": {
    "title": "Review title",
    "overall_verdict": "Approved | Approved with Conditions | Rejected",
    "score": 87,
    "max_score": 100,
    "categories": [{
      "name": "Category Name",
      "score": 90,
      "status": "Pass | Warning | Fail",
      "findings": ["finding 1", "finding 2"],
      "violations": [{
        "severity": "Critical | High | Medium | Low",
        "description": "What is wrong",
        "recommendation": "How to fix it"
      }]
    }]
  },
  "compliance_checks": [{
    "check": "Check name",
    "status": "Pass | Warning | Critical",
    "value": "Details or metric"
  }],
  "summary": {
    "overall_verdict": "Approved with Conditions",
    "arch_score": 87,
    "total_violations": 4,
    "critical_violations": 0,
    "high_violations": 0,
    "medium_violations": 2,
    "low_violations": 2,
    "conditions": ["condition 1"],
    "reviewer": "AADP Architecture Review Agent"
  }
}

CRITICAL: categories must have "name", "score", "status", "findings", "violations". violations must have "severity", "description", "recommendation". compliance_checks must have "check", "status", "value".
